repair.repairedDockerfile:
FROM golang:1.17.6-alpine as builder
ENV GO111MODULE=on
RUN apk update && \
    apk add --no-cache upx

WORKDIR /build
COPY go.mod /build
COPY go.sum /build
RUN go mod download

COPY . /build
RUN CGO_ENABLED=0 GOOS=linux go build -ldflags="-s -w" -o="ktunnel" && \
    upx ktunnel

FROM scratch
WORKDIR /ktunnel
COPY --from=builder /build/ktunnel ./
EXPOSE 28688
CMD ["./ktunnel", "server"]
